[center][img]http://i524.photobucket.com/albums/cc330/Rabrg/Cyberus.jpg[/img][/center]
[center]Cyberus is a 317 based off of [b]Hyperion[/b]. If I don't want to continue this project for a year Ill be needing a couple more programmers to assist me. I plan on running the server after it gets finished, because after all, who wouldn't want to play on a fast, secure server with almost perfect combat and skills?
I'm not going to add over powered bull shit like dragon claws and turmoil, if I wanted those I wouldn't be programming a 317.
If you are interested or want some more information PM me, reply here, or add my MSN: chiddix@live.com[/center]
